Mexican soloists, Mexican and German music, the National Youth Orchestra and a fiery young maestra: The Campus Concert serves up exciting intercultural encounters. Arturo Marquez Leyenda de Miliano Hugo Distler Der Feuerreiter (The Fire Rider) Enrico Chapela Zimmergramm (world premiere) Ludwig van Beethoven Leonore Overture No. 3 Carlos Chavez Caballos de Vapor Salvador Contreras Corridos (encore) Arturo Marquez Danzon Nr. 2 (encore) Pablo Garibay, guitar Marina Unruh, soprano Daniel Todd, tenor Juanra Urrusti, baritone Daniel Pannermayr, bass State Youth Chorus of North Rhine-Westphalia Christiane Zywietz-Godland, choral conductor National Youth Orchestra of Germany Alondra de la Parra, conductor Recorded by Deutsche Welle (DW) in the Beethoven Hall, Bonn September 15, 2016.Composer Enrico Chapela